Manufacturers and architects thus have the opportunity to combine work with care for children.
They are the employees of Arch.Design.They themselves who have imagined this kindergarten and with the support of the management they have obtained a staffing from the European Union and the Ministry of Labour and Social Affairs.
The Mini Maternity School is funded by the European Social Fund through the Operational Programme for Human Resources and the State Budget of the Czech Republic.
